com.camerontec.util.io.externalizer

Class BytesSegmentExternalizerBase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.io.externalizer.BytesSegmentExternalizerBase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The object type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBytesSegmentExternalizer<T>, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BytesSegmentToBytesSegmentExternalizer, ConcurrentStreamingBytesSegmentExternalizerBase, CopyFreeBytesSegmentToBytesSegmentExternalizer

    public abstract class BytesSegmentExternalizerBase<T>
extends Object
implements IBytesSegmentExternalizer<T>
    Base class which provides guaranteed handling for null objects and BytesSegment parameters.

    Handling of null parameters is simplistic:

    • All methods catch null arguments and discontinue if any are found
    • In such cases, methods with return values are guaranteed to return null

    This class also catches and handles any serialization/deserialization exceptions thrown by the underlying implementation.
